<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<openerp>
    <data>
    	<template id="vhr_mysite.update_employee_info" name="Cập nhật thông tin cá nhân">
    		<t t-call="website.layout">
				<div class="update_employee_info container">
					<t t-if="message">
						<div class="my_notices">
							<div class="my_system_notice large">
								<i class="fa fa-check-square-o"></i><span t-esc="message" />
							</div>
						</div>
					</t>
					<div class="update_guide_line">
						<span>Anh/chị vui lòng kiểm tra thông tin cá nhân tại cột “Thông tin hiện tại”, 
						nếu thông tin hiện tại chưa chính xác hoặc cần cập nhật thông tin mới, 
						anh/chị vui lòng điền thông tin mới tại cột “Thông tin cập nhật”. 
						Sau khi kiểm tra thông tin đã đúng hoặc có cập nhật thông tin mới, 
						anh chị vui lòng nhấn "Xác nhận" để hoàn tất.</span> <br /><br />
						<span>Please check your personal information at the column "The current information", 
						if they are note exactly or you need to update the new information, 
						let's input to the next column "The updated information". 
						Then, you submit the "Confirm" box to complete in cases the current information is exactly or they are updated.
						</span>
					</div>
					<t t-if="is_cb">
						<div class="search-info text-center">
							<form id="form-search-info" action="/seach/update_employee_info" method="POST" class="col-xs-12 padding-none">
								<input data-toggle="tooltip" role="tooltip"
			              			class="todo-search-field" data-placement="bottom"
			              			title="Nhập chính xác domain acc hoặc mã nhân viên"
			              			data-delay='{"show":"500", "hide":"100"}'
			              			type="search" value="" placeholder="Tìm kiếm ..."
			              			id="input_info_search"
			              			name="employee_code"
			              			t-att-value="employee_code and employee_code or ''"/>
			              		<i class="fa fa-search fa-lg" id="btn_info_search" ></i>
							</form>
						</div>
					</t>
					<div class="info_title">
		    			THÔNG TIN CÁ NHÂN / PERSONAL INFORMATION
		    		</div>
		    		<form action="/action_update_employee_info" method="post" data-toggle="validator" role="form">
			    		<div class="user_info col-xs-12 form-group">
			    			<div class="col-xs-6">
				    			<span class="info_label">Họ tên / Name: </span>
				    			<input type="text"
										readonly="readonly"
										name="user_name"
										t-att-value="employee.name"
										class="form-control"/>
			    			</div>
			    			<div class="col-xs-6">
			    				<span class="info_label">Mã nhân viên / Employee code: </span>
			    				<input type="text"
										readonly="readonly"
										name="user_code"
										t-att-value="employee.code"
										class="form-control"/>
			    			</div>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4"></div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4 info_label info_label_small text-center">Thông tin hiện tại/Current information</div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4 info_label info_label_small text-center">Thông tin cập nhật (nếu có)/Updated infomation (if any)</div>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line form-group col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4">
								<span class="info_label">1. CMND / ID Number / Passport: </span>
							</div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control"
				    									type="text"
				    									readonly="readonly"
				    									name="user_current_id_number"
				    									t-att-value="id_number and id_number.number or ''"/></div>
				    		<t t-if="id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="text"
				    										name="user_new_id_number"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_id_number or ''"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: 241777888"
				    										maxlength="12"
				    										minlength="8"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
				    		<t t-if="not id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="text"
				    										name="user_new_id_number"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_id_number or ''"
				    										required="required"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: 241777888"
				    										maxlength="12"
				    										minlength="8"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line form-group col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4">
								<span class="info_label pl15">Ngày cấp / Date of issued: </span>
							</div>
				    		
				    		<t t-if="id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4">
				    				<input class="form-control"
	    									type="date"
	    									readonly="readonly"
	    									name="user_current_date_of_issued"
	    									t-att-value="id_number.issue_date and id_number.issue_date or ''"
	    									autocomplete="off"/>
				    			</div>
				    			<div class="col-xs-4">
				    				<input class="form-control edit"
				    						type="date"
				    						name="user_new_date_of_issued"
				    						t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_date_of_issued or ''"
				    						placeholder="Ví dụ: 20/10/2000"
				    						autocomplete="off"/>
				    			</div>
				    		</t>
				    		<t t-if="not id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4">
				    				<input class="form-control"
	    									type="text"
	    									readonly="readonly"
	    									name="user_current_date_of_issued"
	    									value=""
	    									autocomplete="off"/>
	    						</div>
	    						<div class="col-xs-4">
	    							<input class="form-control edit"
    										type="date"
    										name="user_new_date_of_issued"
    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_date_of_issued or ''"
    										required="required"
    										placeholder="Ví dụ: 20/10/2000"
    										autocomplete="off"/>
    							</div>
				    		</t>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line form-group col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4">
								<span class="info_label pl15">Nơi cấp / Place of issued: </span>
							</div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control"
				    									type="text"
				    									readonly="readonly"
				    									name="user_current_place_of_issued"
				    									t-att-value="id_number and id_number.city_id and id_number.city_id.name or ''"
				    									autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		<t t-if="id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    									type="text"
				    									name="user_new_place_of_issued"
				    									t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_place_of_issued or ''"
				    									placeholder="Ví dụ: An Giang"
				    									autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
				    		<t t-if="not id_number">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="text"
				    										name="user_new_place_of_issued"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_place_of_issued or ''"
				    										required="required"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: An Giang"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line form-group col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4">
								<span class="info_label">2. Điện thoại / Phone: </span>
							</div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control"
				    								type="number"
				    								readonly="readonly"
				    								name="user_current_phone" 
				    								t-att-value="employee.mobile"
				    								autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		<t t-if="employee.mobile">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    									type="number"
				    									name="user_new_phone"
				    									t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_phone or ''"
				    									placeholder="Ví dụ: 0987654456"
				    									autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
				    		<t t-if="not employee.mobile">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="number"
				    										name="user_new_phone"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_phone or ''"
				    										required="required"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: 0987654456"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
			    		</div>
			    		<div class="user_info_line form-group col-xs-12">
			    			<div class="col-xs-4">
								<span class="info_label">3. Email cá nhân / Personal email: </span>
							</div>
				    		<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control"
				    										type="email"
				    										readonly="readonly"
				    										name="user_current_email"
				    										t-att-value="employee.email"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		<t t-if="employee.email">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="email"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_email or ''"
				    										name="user_new_email"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: example@gmail.com"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
				    		<t t-if="not employee.email">
				    			<div class="col-xs-4"><input class="form-control edit"
				    										type="email"
				    										name="user_new_email"
				    										t-att-value="update_info and update_info.new_email or ''"
				    										required="required"
				    										placeholder="Ví dụ: example@gmail.com"
				    										autocomplete="off"/></div>
				    		</t>
			    		</div>
			    		<t t-if="employee_code">
							<input style="display:none;" name="render_from_form_search" t-att-value="employee_code"/>		    		
			    		</t>
			    		<div class="col-xs-4"></div>
			    		<div class="form-group col-xs-8 text-center">
						    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"
						    		onclick="return confirm('Bạn chắc chắn những thông tin trên là chính xác?')">XÁC NHẬN / CONFIRM</button>
						</div>
		    		</form>
				</div>
			</t>
    	</template>
   	</data>
</openerp>
